    "description": "A unique RPG game with appealing characters and where your actions have consequences!<br><br>You are Rebecca, an engineer who has had her technology stolen. Your mission: take it back.<br><br>Travel over the world in search of objects and characters that will help you in your mission, through a universe full of challenges!<br><br>Ho, yes... And... Rebecca can reverse the flow of time...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297990/extras/e37c49b126e4dde13bda702b9b83866e.poster.avif?t=1745474521\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297990/extras/e37c49b126e4dde13bda702b9b83866e.webm?t=1745474521\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297990/extras/e37c49b126e4dde13bda702b9b83866e.mp4?t=1745474521\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>(The .gif compression slightly degraded the rendering quality.)</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Intelligent NPCs: they move, talk, never say the same thing twice, notice what you are doing, etc.<br></li><li> Dozens of mini-games, each more addictive than the next.<br></li><li> Original graphics and an unforgettable soundtrack.<br></li><li> An adjustable difficulty, for noobs and pro ;)<br></li><li> 6 to 8 possible endings!</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Your actions have consequences</h2>- You treat John like shit -&gt; He won't like you.<br><br>- You forget to water your plant -&gt; It dies.<br>- You hug someone while being half-naked -&gt; ERECT... Hm... Refusal of the hug.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297990/extras/d55672e5b5d904a6c7cd812ae27d6f43.poster.avif?t=1745474521\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297990/extras/d55672e5b5d904a6c7cd812ae27d6f43.webm?t=1745474521\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297990/extras/d55672e5b5d904a6c7cd812ae27d6f43.mp4?t=1745474521\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>(The .gif compression slightly degraded the rendering quality.)</i><br><br>- You want to play it &quot;psychopath&quot;? -&gt; … Yes… It is possible…<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Warning</h2>Reversed Rebecca is not a horror game. But the player has every right to try to play trash, or worse… This will inevitably have consequences. Be ready to face them.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297990/extras/777b944ae22870ef91b0885760803f99.poster.avif?t=1745474521\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297990/extras/777b944ae22870ef91b0885760803f99.webm?t=1745474521\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297990/extras/777b944ae22870ef91b0885760803f99.mp4?t=1745474521\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>(The .gif compression slightly degraded the rendering quality.)</i>",
